<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.7">
<l>āmiṉ cuvaiyavai yāṟō ṭaṭiciluṇ ṭārntapiṉ</l>
<l>tūmeṉ moḻimaṭa vārirak kappiṉṉun tuṟṟuvār</l>
<l>īmi ṉemakkoru tuṟṟeṉ ṟiṭaṟuva rātaliṉ</l>
<l>kōmiṉ ṟuḻāymuṭi yātiyañ cōti kuṇaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Be [servants]! Those who will eat yet again while women with pure soft words</l>
<l>beg [them], after they have eaten to satiation rice along with [food of] six flavours,</l>
<l>because they will be troubled saying “give us one [bit of] food”,</l>
<l>string the quality of the pretty effulgence beginning with the tulsi crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
